TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT RRMIH.INV_ID, TV.CORP_CD, RRMIH.INV_VER_NB, RRMIH.INV_VER_SEQ_NB, RRMIH.INV_TITL_TXT, RRMIH.INV_STAT_CD, RRMIH.INV_APRV_DT, RRMIH.INV_SENT_DT, RRMIH.INV_RECV_DT, CPDD.PYMT_DUE_DAYS, RRMIH.RBAT_RPT_PRD_ID, RRMIH.NCPDP_VER_CD, RRMIH.RPT_TYP_CD, RRMIH.REMIT_MTHD_CD, RRMIH.MKSR_AGGR_LVL_CD, RRMIH.CNSL_CMPL_CD, RRMIH.TRK_NB, RRMIH.VEND_ID, RRMIH.CO_BE_ID, RRMIH.INV_LOGO_CD, RRMIH.NOTE_TXT, RRMIH.APC_LOAD_CD, RHRMIH.LAST_UPDT_USER_ID, RRMIH.LAST_UPDT_USER_ID, RRMIH.NCPDP_CNSL_CD, RRMIH.NCPDP_LVL_PP_CD, RRMIH.NCPDP_LVL_PN_CN_CD, RRMIH.BASE_DRUG_INCL_CD, RRMIH.CSV_SUMM_CNSL_CD, RRMIH.CSV_SUMM_RBAT_CD, RRMIH.CSV_SUMM_MKSR_CD, RRMIH.CSV_DTL_CNSL_CD, RRMIH.CSV_DTL_MKSR_TYP_CD, RRMIH.CSV_DTL_RBAT_CD, RRMIH.CSV_DTL_VER_CD, RRMIH.LAST_UPDT_TS AS UPDT_TS, RHRMIH.LAST_UPDT_TS AS LAST_UPDT_TS_RCNH
FROM VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR RRMIH
INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNH_RBAT_MFG_INV_HDR RHRMIH ON RRMIH.INV_ID=RHRMIH.INV_ID AND RHRMIH.HIST_INSRT_REAS_CD='I'
INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON RRMIH.VEND_ID=TV.VNDR_ID INNER JOIN (SELECT ID.INV_ID,MAX(TC.PYMT_DUE_DAYS) PYMT_DUE_DAYS FROM VRAP.RCNT_RBAT_MFG_INV_DTL ID, VRAP.TCNTRCT TC WHERE ID.CTRC_ID=TC.CNTRCT_ID GROUP BY ID.INV_ID)CPDD ON CPDD.INV_ID=RRMIH.INV_ID
WHERE RRMIH.LAST_UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS') WITH UR
